  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/ForWard-Technologies-LLC/Pylux</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/ForWard-Technologies-LLC/Pylux/issues</url>
  <description>
    <p>
      Pylux is a free, community-built, open source remote play client forked from Chiaki.
      It focuses on maintaining internet remote play across platforms and aims to keep
      the app easy to access through major app marketplaces. Supports PlayStation 4 and
      PlayStation 5 consoles.
    </p>
  </description>
